[29/01/2019 14:29:19] <font color="#ffffff">Os voy a llevar</font>
[29/01/2019 14:29:19] <font color="#ffffff">a un restaurante africano.</font>
[29/01/2019 14:29:22] <font color="#ffffff">Salam malecum.</font>
[29/01/2019 14:29:23] <font color="#ffffff">-Malecum salam.</font>
[29/01/2019 14:29:26] <font color="#ffffff">-Pues os presento</font>
