[29/01/2019 20:29:05] <font color="#ffff00">Allá vamos.</font>
[29/01/2019 20:29:09] <font color="#ffff00">Eso es.</font>
[29/01/2019 20:29:09] <font color="#ffff00">Fabuloso.</font>
[29/01/2019 20:29:13] <font color="#ffff00">Escurro los tallarines,</font>
